text: Hell in a Cell (2013) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on October 27, 2013 at the American Airlines Arena in Miami, Florida. It was the fifth Hell in a Cell event held by WWE. ==Matches== ==References== ==Other websites== *Official Hell in a Cell 2013 website Category:2013 in professional wrestling Category:World Wrestling Entertainment pay-per-view events Category:Sports in Miami Category:2013 in the United States Category:2010s in Miami
